import React from 'react'; const Skills = () => (

My Skills

Analytical & Strategic Thinking:

Experienced in leading teams and fostering collaboration to achieve team goals in fast-paced environments.

Effective at prioritizing tasks and optimizing workflows to meet tight deadlines and deliver high-quality results.

); export default Skills;
